		<span class="cs6D9F0C8B">&sect;61-3-24d. Fraudulent schemes; cumulation of amounts where common scheme exists; penalties.</span></h4>
	<p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">[Repealed.]</span></p><h4 class="csCA36641A">
		<span class="cs6D9F0C8B">&sect;61-3-24e. Omission to subscribe for workers&rsquo; compensation insurance; failure to file a premium tax report or pay premium taxes; false testimony or statements; failure to file reports; penalties; asset forfeiture; venue.</span></h4>
